description:
Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket smartphones application will be released in 2024!


An app that allows you to easily collect Pokémon cards that are enjoyed all over the world, it also try's to create card interpretation that are only possible along with digital technology. With nostalgic illustrations from the past, and completely new cards that only appear in the app. Stay tuned for an even more widely expanded Pokémon card collection experience!

*All game screens are under development.
title: Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket Official Announcement Trailer

description:
Pokémon Legends: Z-A is the next new entry to the Pokémon video game series, will launch on Nintendo Switch systems in 2025!

A new adventure awaits within Lumiose City, where an urban redevelopment plan is under way to shape the city into a place that belongs to both people and Pokémon.

**NOTE: This trailer does not contain actual game footage.
title: Pokémon Legends: Z-A Official Announcement Trailer
